    "long_instructions": "## Task\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to plan a trip to Disney World. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n\r\n>You’re a travel agent, give me information about Disney World.\r\n\r\n2. Check out this list of **tasks** AI can help with:\r\n    - Summarizing notes\r\n    - Planning an itinerary\r\n    - Drafting an email\r\n3. Revise your prompt to AI Chat by adding in a specific **Task**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n4. Find and complete the section in your Unit Guide called \"Task\". \r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what task to add?**]\r\nTry copy and pasting the following revised prompt into AI Chat: \r\n>You’re a travel agent helping me plan a 5-day trip to Disney World for a family with two young kids. Give me an itinerary for the first day.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
